user: I've been using a meditation app for about three weeks now and I've noticed a significant improvement in my mental clarity and mood. I've been doing 10-minute meditation sessions every morning after stretching for 10-15 minutes. Do you think it's a good idea to increase the duration of my meditation sessions or stick to the current routine?
